data.description: Welcome to 395 S Main, this stately three-family home offers an expansive first floor unit complete with 9 rooms, four/five bedrooms, one full bathroom, plus tons of additional space and an area for potential second bath. Second and Third floor units are two bedroom, one bathroom and well kept. Two units are on gas and one is on oil for heating. There is a bonus carriage building in the rear of the property with a garage, and two-levels of unfinished space that can serve purpose as a workshop, or be finished to offer additional housing space potential. This home sits on .57 acres. Very well maintained home, young roof, updated electrical, replacement windows, must see!
